title: SSIS with on-premises SQL Server
description: This document describes the steps and considerations for extracting data from a Source database and moving it through Staging, Persisted Stage, Data Vault, and Business Data Vault on an on-premise SQL Server.

frontMatter.title: SSIS with on-premises SQL Server
frontMatter.summary: Documentation on steps and considerations for extracting data from a Source database through staging, persisted stage, raw data vault, and business data vault for an on-premise SQL Server
